Usage: addFillerGap [-help] <minGap> [-effort {none low medium high}]
                    [-radius <val>]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
<minGap>                           # minimum gap in microns (float, required)
-effort {none low medium high}     # effort Level (enum, optional)
-radius <val>                      # swap/move search radius (float, optional)